channel.title: 503,508 client with ip changer!
channel.description:
Well title says it all. With this client u can choose wat 503 server u want to connect to and its 100% working. ALL CREDITS TO GRAHAM!!!!
Dl client link: http://www.mediafire.com/?emfirneo2zn Cache dl: http://www.mediafire.com/?vwufz2dqsv6
How to get the client up and working...
- Extract the 503 client.rar to the desktop - Open the 503 client - Open the folder called src - Extract the .jagex_cache_32.rar - Put the cache folder in to it the src folder - Compile the client - Open run and enter the ipadress
I hope it helps
